---
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
import { Download, Trees, ExternalLink, Newspaper } from "lucide-astro";

---

<Navbar />

<main class="min-h-screen bg-white flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-4">Sustainability Training</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">Empowering our community with knowledge for a greener future</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Sections -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl w-full flex flex-col gap-10 text-gray-700">

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <Trees size={28} color="#15803d" />
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-700">Why Sustainability Training?</h2>
  </div>
      <p class="font-light leading-relaxed">
        At IIT Hyderabad, we believe that education is the foundation of lasting change. 
        Our sustainability training programs is designed to equip students, faculty, and staff 
        with the awareness, skills, and tools needed to make environmentally responsible decisions 
        both on campus and beyond.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <Trees size={28} color="#15803d" />
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-700">What the Training Covers</h2>
  </div>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside font-light leading-relaxed space-y-2">
        <li>Introduction to the UN's 17 Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs)</li>
        <li>IITH's climate action framework and sustainability policy</li>
        <li>Energy conservation and renewable energy practices</li>
        <li>Waste management, composting, and zero-waste strategies</li>
        <li>Water conservation and recycling initiatives</li>
        <li>Green campus infrastructure and biodiversity</li>
        <li>Student-led sustainability programs and how to get involved</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

       <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <Trees size={28} color="#15803d" />
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-700">Who Is It For?</h2>
  </div>
        This training is open to all members of the IITH community incoming students, 
        research scholars, faculty, and administrative staff. It is also shared with 
        partner institutions and the broader public as part of IITH's outreach mission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-2">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <Trees size={28} color="#15803d" />
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-700">Our Commitment</h2>
  </div>
        IITH is committed to integrating sustainability into every aspect of institutional life. 
        Through the School for Sustainable Science and Technology and the Climate Action Committee, 
        we continuously develop programs that inspire action and measure real-world impact.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>

  <!-- Download Button -->
  <!-- <div class="mt-16 mb-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">Download our full training presentation below</p>
    <a 
      href="/assets/files_data/Sustainability at IITH.pptx"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-200"
    >
      <Download size={20} />
      Sustainability At IITH
    </a>
  </div> -->

  <div class="mt-16 mb-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
    View our full training presentation below
  </p>

  <a 
    href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/189ujwU3_nb3gyd-SmCpwUelcc90A93AbUiknB4D10GA/view"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-200"
  >
    <Download size={20} />
    Sustainability Presentation
  </a>
</div>

 <div class=" mb-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
  <p class="text-orange-400 text-sm italic">
    After going through the presentation, please perform a self-assessment on your sustainability awareness.
  </p>

  <a 
    href="https://moodle.cse.iith.ac.in/moodle/mod/quiz/view.php?id=1077"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-200"
  >
    <Newspaper size={20} />
    Sustainability Assessment
  </a>
</div>

</main>

<Footer />